    {
      title: 'Customer Management Advisor at NGA Human Resources',
      description: 'Managed payroll and HR operations for multiple clients, ensuring accuracy and compliance. Optimized workforce administration, streamlined processes, and enhanced the customer experience through problem-solving and data management.',
